##DESCRIPTION
##  Plug a value into a formula from a word problem 
##
##ENDDESCRIPTION
## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Algebra of real numbers and simplifying expressions)
## DBsection(Evaluating expressions)
## Institution(The College of Idaho)
